                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18090111-63-defend642 t18090111-63-punish384"></join>
               Publicly whipped near the West India Docks
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>WITSCH, <rs id="t18090111-63-verdict385" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18090111-63-verdict385" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>, aged 45.</p>
